How many hours and at what times do you play each week?
<p><center><textarea name="answer1" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Afterlife raid times are 1730 (5:30pm) PST until 2400 (midnight)
PST, every day.  While we don't regularly raid this much, the
potential is there.  What times can you raid?
<p><center><textarea name="answer2" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Do you meet entrance requirements?  If not, why?
<p><center><textarea name="answer3" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Game play test: Your group is approaching a pack of five challenging
elite NPC's.  Pick five classes and describe exactly what each class
does during the fight, and why.  Note: there is no perfect answer.
<p><center><textarea name="answer4" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Humor test: Two antennas meet, fall in love, and get married.  People
afterwards say the ceremony was beautiful, but the reception was
terrible.  Your reaction:
<p><center><textarea name="answer5" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Riddle test: You are given a 5 gallon jug and a 3 gallon jug and
sent down to a river to return with exactly one gallon.  You don't
have any other measuring devices, you can't mark on the jugs, and
the gallon has to be exact.  How do you do it?
<p><center><textarea name="answer6" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Social graces: List all Afterlife members you know, and how you
know them.  Also list what you like best about each one.  Optionally
list what you like least about each one.
<p><center><textarea name="answer7" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

History: What other games have you played?  How long did you play
them?  What classes/professions/etc. did you choose?  What level
did you achieve?  What guilds did you join, and why?  Why did you
leave?  What raiding have you done?
<p><center><textarea name="answer8" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>
<p>
